divs: Sighting Details I was out trying to take pictures of the sun. So I decided to just take a video of the sun because I have seen alot of videos that supposedly have Nibru in them. I never noticed what was on this video until I watched it on my digital camera. The UFO or object starts to appear on this video as soon as I start recording. It starts to appear on the left bottom of the screen on the video. I don't know where it came from or what it is doing but it looks like it is just circling around and around the sun. You will have to look at this frame by frame because it is so fast.
Summary: UFO/ Object flying around and near the Sun
